data.description: Wonderful ranch home located in Forest Park. This 4-sided brick home has vinyl plank flooring throughout, with granite tops, and tile bathrooms.  Additionally, a great location with easy access to shops and restaurants. Just a few minutes from Hartsfield-Jackson International Airport. Walk out to back to private backyard with large shed with a huge loft that can be used for additional storage or workshop space (504+ square feet).  Great home for the price!  (No Disclosure - Sold as is with right to inspect).      (Seller willing to pay up to 3% of buyer's closing costs if under contract by November 3)
